OL,3,CThe government doesn't want to change
OL,4,Cthe law on whole life terms - here's
OL,5,Cwhy
OL,7,FThe reason is simple: the only way to
OL,8,Fimprison someone forever is to impose
OL,9,Fa "whole life order" and while Tories
OL,10,Freduced the age of eligibility for
OL,11,Fthis sentence from 21 to 18, in order
OL,12,Fto apply it to a perpetrator in the
OL,13,FManchester bombing, it is not
OL,14,Favailable for those below 18.
OL,16,FRudakubana committed this atrocity
OL,17,Fnine days before his 18th birthday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
