OL,3,CThe government doesn't want to change
OL,4,Cthe law on whole life terms - here's
OL,5,Cwhy
OL,7,FToday, the Conservatives called for
OL,8,Fthe law to change so that - in
OL,9,Fexceptional circumstances like this
OL,10,Fone - a whole life tariff could apply.
OL,12,FShock at the sentence has triggered a
OL,13,Freview of it by the UK's Law Officers
OL,14,F- the Attorney and Solicitor General.
OL,15,FBut the Government has made clear
OL,16,Ftoday that it will not change the
OL,17,Frules so that minors can be subject to
OL,18,Fa whole life sentence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
