OL,3,CThe government doesn't want to change
OL,4,Cthe law on whole life terms - here's
OL,5,Cwhy
OL,7,FBut are they right - can they really
OL,8,Fnot change the law?
OL,10,FIt is clear to me - from speaking to
OL,11,Flegal figures who have held senior
OL,12,Fpositions in Government, former
OL,13,FCabinet ministers and the types of
OL,14,Fhuman rights lawyers who would take a
OL,15,Fcase against such a decision that if
OL,16,FKeir Starmer wants to make this
OL,17,Fchange, he can.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
