OL,3,CThe government doesn't want to change
OL,4,Cthe law on whole life terms - here's
OL,5,Cwhy
OL,7,FAnd it is this second point that would
OL,8,Fpull back Keir Starmer, a former
OL,9,Flawyer with the norms of international
OL,10,Flaw running through his blood. Yes the
OL,11,FUK could breach international law -
OL,12,Fand get away with it - but he would
OL,13,Fnot want that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
